# For VS Code REST Client / JetBrains HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Login (JWT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin1@ocp.com",
  "password": "CHANGE_ME"
}

### Refresh (JWT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

### Me
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Validations - Voyages (Responsable service)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/responsable/service/voyages?typePaie=mensuelle&status=submitted
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Batch validate voyages (service)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/responsable/service/voyages/batch/validate
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

### Batch reject voyages (service)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/responsable/service/voyages/batch/reject
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

### Batch retour voyages (service -> gestionnaire)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/responsable/service/voyages/batch/retour
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

### Validations - Prime performance (Responsable service)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/responsable/service/prime-performance?typePaie=mensuelle&status=submitted
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Batch validate prime performance (service)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/responsable/service/prime-performance/batch/validate
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [10, 11]
}

### Validations - Prime fonction (Responsable service)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/responsable/service/prime-fonction?typePaie=mensuelle&status=submitted
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN
